name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForLiverDiseases
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Liver Diseases
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to any kind of liver (hepatic) disease.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes any kind of liver (hepatic) disease. Includes acute hepatic failure, acute and chronic hepatitis, cirrhosis, as well as structural/anatomic abnormalities such as cysts and nodules.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes liver transplantation.)
